name: Chartreux/British Shorthair - 藍貓
description:
更新了更新了 v2 v2 v2!!!
Lora trained based on 45 distinct 512x512 Chartreux (British Shorthair/藍貓) Photos from one of my favorite Chartreux from 抖音(叫聲喵主子)。


For best results, you may follow the setting

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

Steps: 20+

Lora Weight: 0.4-0.7

Model: MagicMix Realistic v6 for Realistic pictures

These are the possible prompts:

Must - Trigger Word: Chartreux, cat

Actions: Open Mouth, Lying, Jumping from above, flying cat, hand pov, angry face

Clothes : Please use <c4ttitudeflexver> to assist you with clothing, it will yield the best results

提示 - 提示詞：

必須：Chartreux, cat

不同動作: Open Mouth, Lying, Jumping from above, flying cat, hand pov, angry face

衣服: 可以使用 <c4ttitudeflexver> 以便換上不同的衣服

為獲得最佳效果，您可以遵循以下設置

取樣器：DPM++ SDE Karras

步驟：20+

Lora權重：0.4-0.7

模型：MagicMix Realistic v6 以用於生成真實圖片
